Install procedure
-----------------

        % gzip -cd at-spi-1.9.0.tar.gz | tar xvf -  # unpack the sources
        % cd at-spi-1.9.0                           # change to the toplevel directory
        % ./configure                               # run the `configure' script
        % make                                      # build at-spi

        [ Become root if necessary ]
        % make install                              # install at-spi

Requirements
------------

        GNU make
        GNU autotools

        pkg-config

        python

        glib
        gtk+
        gail

        dbus
        dbus-glib
        dbus-python

        X
        XEVIE (Reccomended)
